data.description: Take in the stunning mountain views from this immaculate property!  The home features newer luxury vinyl flooring & carpet, spacious & open kitchen with breakfast bar, master has a stunning 5-piece bath, custom wood features throughout and a separate office. Outside find a large patio & fenced in yard with dog run, 2 car garage, 2400 sq ft fully insulated outbuilding w/14X16 door on remote, wood burning heat & 220 electric, corral w/chute, lean-to & concrete feed bunks - perfect for 4-H projects! No HOA or covenants!  Peaceful country living with an easy drive to Greeley or Denver.
